207
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:39,014
What are you going to do?

208
00:11:39,682 --> 00:11:41,683
Shall we do it with just
the two of us then?

209
00:11:51,694 --> 00:11:54,329
After Yuka turned them down,
Junko and Hitomi got down

