write it down right away.

215
00:12:18,721 --> 00:12:21,690
Solidifying your movements
a little at a time.

216
00:12:25,061 --> 00:12:27,596
It's also important to build
up your muscles, so you can

217
00:12:27,597 --> 00:12:30,799
